  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Humanitarian assistance programme in Afghanistan</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The objective of the proposed project is to continue supporting IOM Afghanistan&#x2019;s Humanitarian Assistance Program (HAP), implementing modifications to enhance the impact and consolidate the gains of the activities undertaken in the last seven years. Proposed activities: 1. Providing emergency relief assistance for vulnerable natural disaster or conflict affected/displaced populations; 2. Strengthening State Ministry for Disaster Management and Humanitarian Affairs/Afghanistan National Disaster Management Authority (SMDMHA/ANDMA) institutional capacities and providing technical support 3. Enhancing community based disaster risk management capacities by conducting non-structural community based disaster risk management (CBDRM) activities at community level in selected provinces.</narrative>
  </description>
